socketfun - chat
----------------

This accomplishes a chat server and clients that can chat with each other.
Error checking is not performed for purpose of brevity and readability.

build instructions
--------------------------
$ gcc -o chatserver -lpthread -std=c90 -Wall chatserver.c
$ gcc -o chatclient -lpthread -std=c90 -Wall chatclient.c

or do

$ make

running
-------
$ ./chatserver

On different teminals

$ ./chatclient

commands
--------
ls - to get list of users currently connected to the server

send <username> <msg> - to send a message to a particular user

exit - to disconnect from the server

clean up
--------
$ make clean
